Q-2) Write a Java program to reverse a string

Input = “java”

Output = “avaj”


class ReverseString {

    public static void main(String[] args) {

        String s = "java";
        String rev = "";

        for (int i = s.length() - 1; i >= 0; i--) {
            rev = rev + s.charAt(i);
        }

        System.out.println(rev);
    }
}
